{"talk":{"id":60774,"name":"Mary Ellen Hannibal: How you can help save the monarch butterfly -- and the planet","description":"Monarch butterflies are dying at an alarming rate around the world -- a looming extinction that could also put human life at risk. But we have just the thing to help save these insects, says author Mary Ellen Hannibal: citizen scientists. Learn how these grassroots volunteers are playing a crucial role in measuring and rescuing the monarch's dwindling population -- and how you could join their ranks to help protect nature. (You'll be in good company: Charles Darwin was a citizen scientist!)","slug":"mary_ellen_hannibal_how_you_can_help_save_the_monarch_butterfly_and_the_planet","recorded_at":"2019-12-04 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-04-01 15:01:51","updated_at":"2022-04-12 19:48:18","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":618,"name":"TEDWomen 2019"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/22048994aa7002bd0fc515bfd2cefc5ee8c18962_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/22048994aa7002bd0fc515bfd2cefc5ee8c18962_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/22048994aa7002bd0fc515bfd2cefc5ee8c18962_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/22048994aa7002bd0fc515bfd2cefc5ee8c18962_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/a38e98436d291a162abf344cdcc57c99a7f36da1_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MaryEllenHannibal_2019W-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":5908203,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MaryEllenHannibal_2019W-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":16359901,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MaryEllenHannibal_2019W-320k.mp4?a